{"id": "1196112530406391949", "channel_id": "1196112530406391949", "type": 0, "author_id": "998266367650308108", "author_name": "banano.2", "author_bot": false, "content": "摸摸看，拆件花最多時間 😂 \n官方沒有給立繪所以我拿遊戲截圖跟官方的預告圖拼好後再去背 (鐮刀被卡掉不管了)\nUID : 100174516", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T15:24:09.945000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-17T05:22:31.231000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 25}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}], "attachments": [{"id": "1196112532004413440", "filename": "4.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 12013136, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196112530406391949/1196112532004413440/4.mp4?ex=69cbe71a&is=69ca959a&hm=3293fb37641bee6d9403a9b736ced0ec74e75914bef55476afeb57799040f280&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1196112530406391949", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "索蕾爾動態立繪", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811", "1182359901335470100"]}
