{"id": "1196132481007628328", "channel_id": "1196112530406391949", "type": 0, "author_id": "428521987934257164", "author_name": "chuchiyung", "author_bot": false, "content": "🛐用什麼軟體做的 有教學？😂", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T16:43:26.539000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1196112530406391949", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "索蕾爾動態立繪", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811", "1182359901335470100"]}
{"id": "1196140474960969760", "channel_id": "1196112530406391949", "type": 19, "author_id": "998266367650308108", "author_name": "banano.2", "author_bot": false, "content": "AE喔！\n拆物件用就用熟悉的繪圖軟體就好了(我是用CSP)但一次存圖PS比較好用，所以建議用可以存PS檔的繪圖軟體\n\n拆完就扔進AE裡面調\n\n**圖1-圖2 **-主要是用這兩個插件(AFP/AutoSway)來做服裝/頭髮的動態 (用法都一樣，錨點點點點+參數調調調，固定不要動的地方把動畫刪掉)\n\n**圖3** - 一些小地方的的擺動(最下面的裙襬/鐮刀的絲帶)就用AE內建的Turbulent Displacement這個效果\n\n**圖4** - 剩下一些簡單的上下擺動/旋轉/放大縮小 就用內建的wiggle三個系列就能實現了🤣 (像是胸口要像呼吸一樣放大縮小就wiggle scale 鐮刀要有搖晃的感覺就wiggle rotate)\n\n**圖5** - 把物件分類comp(群組)這樣才不會很難找到哪個物件在哪&我都習慣分 頭/身體/下半身 /其他有需要在加 這樣要做律動感也比較方便(直接在comp塞個wiggle position動起來就會比較自然) \n－\n大概就這樣！但我也不是專業的所以只會一些基礎的技巧，只能做這種基本動態（呼吸開閉眼睛之類的  😂 ），官方那種的才是真的猛。網路上應該能挖到更多複雜的教學～", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T17:15:12.446000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-14T17:17:28.071000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["428521987934257164"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1196140473568481431", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5928, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196112530406391949/1196140473568481431/image.png?ex=69cc0120&is=69caafa0&hm=be66829b510f773697d6bc502a1e4ad755f2f8ddf73c762067ec6f5610372d02&"}, {"id": "1196140473820127423", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 231649, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196112530406391949/1196140473820127423/image.png?ex=69cc0120&is=69caafa0&hm=24981f6dcbc9931317b92db2f597c3eb55df048d925dddc263114229f84d9028&"}, {"id": "1196140474067583007", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 223791, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196112530406391949/1196140474067583007/image.png?ex=69cc0120&is=69caafa0&hm=1d8639457d1cec64cad095f2630d4f708c76dd3c6f72e2f24be302b4504b0076&"}, {"id": "1196140474411536384", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 8052, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196112530406391949/1196140474411536384/image.png?ex=69cc0120&is=69caafa0&hm=fae834f578330963bd3730e559736d8a755c97e948170cc1072adfcf4d4a71e7&"}, {"id": "1196140474793205820", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 228833, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1196112530406391949/1196140474793205820/image.png?ex=69cc0120&is=69caafa0&hm=f54a9762b1164ebd17a528a23e7051d29acf38f91cc39c5b9e24ca211fd99630&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1196132481007628328", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1196112530406391949", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "索蕾爾動態立繪", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811", "1182359901335470100"]}
{"id": "1195920284620955788", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "HE 終結末日", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:40:14.978000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920323896426556", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:40:24.342000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1195920323460206623", "filename": "IMG_0209.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3693480, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1193218276898127872/1195920323460206623/IMG_0209.png?ex=69cbdcd8&is=69ca8b58&hm=e20c4fe058c9dfb3ce6194c5ae5c61ad2139be693164048561deeca020e3f3ef&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920379210903582", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實照設定來看 應該要有三結局\n壞結局>>同化\n假結局>>進化\n真結局>>終結末日\n但我想去下個世界 所以懶了 哈哈", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:40:37.530000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920490041188444", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "補充設定：\n\n血肉世界觀下每個人出生就已被血肉污染，隨著年紀的增長，會產生進化與同化，兩者差異在於為個人意識的多寡。", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:41:03.954000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920568130732032", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然說是污染，但也就是心理學上本我、超我之間的拉扯，結果即為自我，本我我設定類似生物精神體，人物設定有每個人的精神體種類，在真結局中D找到分離的辦法，所以大多數普通人能經過手術將生物精神體分割出來，達到斬草除根的效果。", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:41:22.572000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920699152416788", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "精神體分開後就算是兩個個體了", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:41:53.810000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920758015279114", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "可以選擇共同生活或分開\n但相互之間還是能互相感應", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:42:07.844000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920816827801650", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "至於慾望的部分還是會有的\n但精神體分離後就不會出現想想就能變強的狀況", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:42:21.866000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920872117108828", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "末日的故事很簡單 \n主要團體分為實驗室、新人類研究所、傭兵團", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:42:35.048000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920915217797120", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "實驗室為保守勢力，像大多數末日世界中選擇修築高牆建造要塞，以牆內生活為主的人們，有自己的戰力，會與其他要塞組成聯合政府，簽訂契約的要塞不可在沒有公告的情況下互相攻擊", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:42:45.324000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195920961732620408", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "新人類研究所相較於實驗室，更趨向向外開拓資源的人們，一樣會建立組織，但大多數以車隊進行移動，有特殊發現時才會帶回研究院內，基本一生花費在探索之中", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:42:56.414000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195921003675648100", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "傭兵團\n有錢能使鬼推磨代表 魚龍混雜地區\n實驗室與研究所想做些較為骯髒危險事時的委託選擇，處於互相看不起的狀態", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:43:06.414000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:44:17.492000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195921077017268265", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "主線劇情大綱：\n\n實驗室將LILY視為許願機器囚禁在地下室內，結果卻被即將廢棄的實驗體H帶走並逃脫，於是派出手下進行追捕，D為實驗體H的主要研究者，所以被強制外派了，過程中其實是被隊友丟包但自認為只是走散，途中遇到Y並雇用她作為保鑣，之後遇到早該被血肉同化的實驗體H與母體L，得知有抑制血肉的辦法後，在L的幫助下開始研究，將訊息傳回實驗室卻反而被通緝，其原因為既得利益者不願放下手中權勢，想讓血肉末日繼續下去，之後四人在研究所的幫助下尋獲關鍵素材，成功完成血肉分離辦法，末日終結", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:43:23.900000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:45:02.174000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195921136916107404", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "壞結局-同化\nY與D到地下溶洞尋找素材，遭遇實驗室與溶洞怪物的攻擊、Y為掩護D戰至被血肉同化，而D則在追擊過程中失去左腿，並被素材迷失心智，成為溶洞之主，另一方面，藏於廢棄實驗室的H與L也遭受實驗室的大量攻擊，由於大量的人與慾望的湧入(此時所有人都知道L的能力，每個人都想許願），L最終選擇實現所有人的願望，但願望過於龐大，所以只能在在夢境中實現，因此所有人都在廢棄實驗室內長眠，H成為區域中的巡視幽靈，斬殺一切有自主意識的生命，因為夢中不該有人醒著", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:43:38.181000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195921183187669012", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "假結局-進化\n知曉血肉力量的本源，剩餘的人類開始肉體與精神的雙修之路，看似美好的未來即將到來，但被精神壓抑在血肉之下另一個視線亦在蠢蠢欲動", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:43:49.213000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1195921226439348295", "channel_id": "1193218276898127872", "type": 0, "author_id": "726975907449012274", "author_name": "sofakiwi_0228", "author_bot": false, "content": "真結局-末日終結\n完美規避所有死亡flag \n田園生活 啟動！", "timestamp": "2024-01-14T02:43:59.525000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193218276898127872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Morimens平行宇宙論", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
